Version 1.1 (18 April 2016)

[General]

  * introduced support for multiple Base OS versions:
     - CentOS 7.2
     - SLES12 SP1
  * enable support in Warewulf for ECDSA ssh host keys (Issue https://github.com/openhpc/ohpc/issues/202)
  * updated OpenMPI configuration to support Grid Engine (Issue https://github.com/openhpc/ohpc/issues/192)
  * modified recipe test logic for enable_<feature> options (Issue https://github.com/openhpc/ohpc/issues/147)
  * variety of clarifications and expansions in recipe documentation including:
      - configuration examples for new component additions
      - availability of wwnodescan
      - example diskfull configuration for CentOS7.2 (not applicable for SLES)
      - addition of new Appendix to highlight process of rebuilding packages from source

[Component Additions]

  * clustershell-ohpc                        (1.7.1)
  * genders-compat-ohpc                      (1.22)
  * genders-ohpc                             (1.22)
  * mrsh-ohpc                                (2.7)
  * mrsh-rsh-compat-ohpc                     (2.7)
  * mrsh-server-ohpc                         (2.7)
  * ocr-gnu-ohpc                             (1.0.1)
  * ocr-intel-ohpc                           (1.0.1)
  * shine-ohpc                               (1.4)
  * spack-ohpc                               (0.8.17)
  * vim-clustershell-ohpc                    (1.7.1)

